        "version_name": "圣经当代译本",
        "lang": "chs",
        "text": "波斯王塞鲁士元年，耶和华为要应验祂借耶利米所说的话，就感动波斯王塞鲁士，使他下诏通告全国："
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "波斯王古列元年，耶和華為要應驗他藉耶利米的口所說的話，就激動波斯王古列的心靈，使他通令全國，傳達文告說："
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "波斯王塞魯士元年，耶和華為要應驗藉耶利米口所說的話，就激動波斯王塞魯士的心，使他下詔通告全國說："
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Now in the first year of Cyrus king of Persia, in order to fulfill the word of the Lord by the mouth of Jeremiah, the Lord stirred up the spirit of Cyrus king of Persia, so that he sent a proclamation throughout all his kingdom, and also put it in writing, saying:"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "In the first year of Cyrus king of Persia, in order to fulfill the word of the Lord spoken by Jeremiah, the Lord moved the heart of Cyrus king of Persia to make a proclamation throughout his realm and also to put it in writing:"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "In the first year of King Cyrus of Persia, the Lord fulfilled the prophecy he had given through Jeremiah. He stirred the heart of Cyrus to put this proclamation in writing and to send it throughout his kingdom:"
      }
